# Project Rules

## Styling and UI
This project uses **shadcn/ui** and **Tailwind CSS**. All styling should follow the component-based approach defined in `.cursor/rules/styling.md`.

- **UI Components**: Use `@/components/ui` for primitives.
- **Styling**: Use Tailwind utility classes. Avoid custom CSS.
- **Theme**: Use theme variables from `tailwind.config.ts`.
- **Conditional Classes**: Use the `cn` utility from `@/lib/utils`.

## Tech Stack
- React (Vite)
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS
- shadcn/ui
- Lucide React (Icons)
- Radix UI (Primitives)

